                            <comment id="418211" author="adilger" created="Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:53:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This should be fixed in interop testing by the most recent ATM-3021 patch. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="417715" author="adilger" created="Thu, 13 Jun 2024 23:17:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This subtest should be skipped on interop testing with older branches.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="408744" author="adilger" created="Sat, 23 Mar 2024 01:45:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sebastien, I&apos;m seeing a lot of sanity-sec test_55 failures that are being attributed to this ticket:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/search?status%5B%5D=FAIL&amp;amp;test_set_script_id=5984404e-4b34-11e0-a7f6-52540025f9af&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=72320fcc-bee0-41a2-8f48-624be12babc9&amp;amp;start_date=2024-03-16&amp;amp;end_date=2024-03-22&amp;amp;source=sub_tests#redirect&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/search?status%5B%5D=FAIL&amp;amp;test_set_script_id=5984404e-4b34-11e0-a7f6-52540025f9af&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=72320fcc-bee0-41a2-8f48-624be12babc9&amp;amp;start_date=2024-03-16&amp;amp;end_date=2024-03-22&amp;amp;source=sub_tests#redirect&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not sure if this is the same issue, or if a new one should be opened?  They are all failing testing with master servers, though some sessions with b_es6_0 clients are also failing, if that helps you isolate the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="361526" author="sebastien" created="Fri, 3 Feb 2023 14:34:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, this can be due to a missing patch on b2_12, that aims at improving the test. I have ported it:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/49891&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/49891&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="361408" author="adilger" created="Thu, 2 Feb 2023 18:04:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sebastien, it looks like this subtest is failing regularly during interop testing with &quot;&lt;tt&gt;fileset not taken into account&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;.  Is this something to be concerned about, or something unexpected in the interop testing that should be skipped?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please take a look.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
